uote><blockquote>有無巴絲起到佢ig同相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw咁樣無咁樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPrivated"},{"pid":"f9ec60c87b0c1fa124539d5e7dd602b02e6614b7","tid":260291,"uid":65256,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"想講好耐 條女真係好差呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先講樣 佢隻眼好撚奇怪 眼珠一邊大一邊細<br />\n好撚恐怖<br />\n個鼻又肉酸 啲頭髮又成個假髮咁<br />\n有波都冇用啦<br />\n之後講戲 佢啲戲真係睇到我起曬雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扮發脾氣扮到成個燥狂症病人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果幕係嬲到勁撚突然 一啲先兆都唔比<br />\n仲要嬲到鬧到好似想揸刀劈你咁 真心好恐怖<br />\n睇到我勁不安<br />\n之後再一秒扮番死狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬呀 睇撚到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋一開頭大嗌果度 讀對白之餘 又係唔理解點解要嗌到成個精神病人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c71cd657b614aa46d80d7bddc148b53f920c19b","tid":260291,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"兩個字：唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢搞到我投入唔到"},{"pid":"bfc9a759faca91b7d08b98a91613433946cb144b","tid":260291,"uid":61560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"係咪得我覺得熊仔頭啲電影仔都唔好睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc85464dd536a0c1d192106ed1e42132041ed75e","tid":260291,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只係唔算靚姐<br />\n講到條女真係好柒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒到飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94022eafd3fa586565c583cb479a7d3d05632ebc","tid":260291,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:25:23.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7561dc74384bfd78318f258530cc78881eefc4c1","tid":260291,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪得我覺得熊仔頭啲電影仔都唔好睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係差左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas